6 4250   Kent. Break, heart; I prithee break!
6 4251   Edg. Look up, my lord.
6 4252   Kent. Vex not his ghost. O, let him pass! He hates him
6 4253      That would upon the rack of this tough world
6 4254      Stretch him out longer.
